Transformation Notes: [Manifestation]-->rdamd:P30004-->"(ISBN)" + {value of $a} + "({value of $q})" + " ; " + "({value of $q})" -- ZP 5/29/2022; Combine multiple $q values; if no punctuation in the record, enclose all occurences of $q in one set of parentheses and separate individual values with " ; " -- ZP 6/14/2022

[Manifestation]-->rdamd:P30004-->"(Canceled/invalid ISBN)" + {value of $z} + "({value of $q})" + " ; " + "({value of $q})" -- ZP 5/29/2022; Combine multiple $q values; if no punctuation in the record, enclose all occurences of $q in one set of parentheses and separate individual values with " ; " -- ZP 6/14/2022
